#
# Purpose:
# - Validate ATR filter candidates using trade logs generated by Event Filter v2.
# - Compare ATR OFF / P60 / P65 / P70 / P75 / Lookback 250/500/750.
# - Compare mainly:
#   1) Current Event: Candidate A date_all_day
#   2) Candidate Event: Candidate C hybrid policy
#
